modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod allows to all trees respawn including cactus. Into seedlings / breakable / regrow via game stages. Cactus become ghostly and [respawn](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-respawn/) after 5 Days.

* The regrowth rate is what pimps set it to 300.
* Less seeds from all [trees](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-trees/)
* Lower % chance of getting seeds from trees so itâ€™s not overcrowded.(balance is very important else high level players are abusing the orignal system)

**Update**  
Added spruce trees to the list and balanced.

**[Download](https://botmanhosting.com/A18/HH_All_Types_Of_Trees_Respawn.zip)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11963-highopes-modlets/).
